0.text: Tara rung kaw madat la ai lam gaw ntsen ai wa a lawan ladan tara rung kaw jep yu na ahkaw ahkang hte seng nna masat mahtoi hpe ma matsing tawn da wa sai.

1.text: Dai hpawt maga hta, nbung ni gaw 83km/h daram rai nga nna dai nbung ni bai ngya wa na ngu myit mada lai wa sai.

2.text: Hkum kaw na sai hpe gayin ya ai gaw salum re, shi gaw dsai hpe tu ya ai re.

3.text: Dai website hpe masha grai ra ma ai, hpaji tam ai ni grau re.

4.text: Bu hkawm ai magam gaw masha uhpung kaba ni a matu gaw grau manu hpa ai re. Dai majaw lama na nang hkrai sha manang langai hte sha rai yang gaw, masha langai hkrai a manu gau hkyemsa na matu mali kaw na kru du hkra re ai masha uhpung hkrang pru wa hkra laga masha ni hte hkrum tsup na matu shakut u.

5.text: Nkau camera kasha ni gaw 6 by 6 cm format hpe lang ma ai, 56 by 56 mm negative gaw grau hkrak ai re.

6.text: Na a asak pahkam hkrang tara ni hte rau pahkam hkam ya ai wa hpe matut mahkai mai na ahkri ahkrai ni hpe atsawm galaw da na dai laika ni a kanan ni hpe mung gun hkawm u.

7.text: Jahpawt hta na nta ting manu dan ai kaphi lu nna shana gaw chamomile hpalap lu nna shalan shabran u.

8.text: Bum ntsa kaw na numri tawng gaw shihkrai numri bum ntsa kaw na dik hkrak wa chye ai baw re.

9.text: Shang gumhpraw ahkun hta ai lam gaw mungdan langai hte langai nbung ai re, ngut nna ahkun manu ni gaw mungdan hte langai grai shai ma ai.
